Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the main base of Captain M'Quve, who\Ncontrols Earth's greatest mineral resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is M'Quve's main base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.55,0:01:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...is steadily preparing for Operation Odessa,\Nan attack on this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base is continuing westward...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to join this operation. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:02:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...the assault from Ramba Ral's soldiers\Nis not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow and Hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One worn-out old Zaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...and four Magella Attack gun turrets?\NIs that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems clear that Captain M'Quve\Nis not being cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Lt. Tachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to avenge Ral, no matter the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We feel the same, Ms. Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Tachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The scouts have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse's back is to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- That gives us an opportunity to attack.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the damage to the Trojan Horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.40,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're working desperately on repairs,\Nbut they have very few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's hurry. Get on with the preparations.\N- Yes, Ms. Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship won't last\Nif we keep taking hits like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're low on parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons are running low too.\NWe've got to plan resupplies at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't complain, Hayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can't predict what'll happen{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll survive using our wits and ingenuity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our wits and ingenuity, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not use Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't say that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- How are you?\N- Well, so so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, condition poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, condition poor. Ryu, condition poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Haro!\N- It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.31,0:04:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Haro sure is well made.\NAnd honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haro is well.\NRyu, get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.78,0:04:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Haro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's even programmed to be flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything you want me to do, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do me a favor and tell everyone\NI'm getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me... Is it true that Bright\Nput Amuro back in solitary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Amuro the one who's being stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magella Tops have been\Nrigged to the Cargo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Gallop's spare engine,\Nit can travel at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have the Zaku carry\Na Magella Top's main gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have two Samsons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 16 soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...all loyal men with long service\Nto Ramba Ral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the excellent preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to Earth to avenge\Nthe death of Lord Garma, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have not yet completed the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At first glance, this is a small operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the enemy is the Federation's\Nmost advanced warship and mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Zeon have\Ngreat expectations of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...such an honorable man that\NI may not have deserved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's to avenge the man who loved me so,\NI won't regret dying in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who object to this operation\Nneed not participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral won't hold it against you.\NNeither will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no concern about that, Ms. Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is committed to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Torgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ms. Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ms. Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Illusin, I want you to do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. I'll avenge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu...! Your wounds won't heal\Nif you're moving around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I should move my body a bit,\Nor it won't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you all right?\N- Well... It's about Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If we act as though we're counting on him,\Nhis head will swell even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true. Right, Ms. Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. But there are rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a wild tiger will realize his position\Nif you leave him in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're going to wait\Nuntil Amuro figures things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like you're making excuses to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making excuses? How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings can use words.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So while I'm still well enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, what are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never really talked to Amuro,\Nhave you, Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The tiger will never be tamed then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Sunmalo or Sayla.\NReturn Ryu to his bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that boy gets In the way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...my dear...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...please protect me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Now we just have to adjust\Nthe magnetic pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a pilot, and getting enough sleep{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Were you awake...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I was wondering...\NNow that Bright put you back in solitary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't you resent him for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand Mr. Bright's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He's afraid of you,\Ncomparing you to a wild tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A wild tiger...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, I have hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you up and about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was over here at Amuro's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Ryu going to be all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine.\NDon't worry about him, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a drill attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A tried and true method\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our first strike hits what seems\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We focus on just one spot, ignoring all else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our survival will not be certain, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we can surely destroy the Trojan Horse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect. Damn Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! They're behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From where? Where's the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They want to take down the White Base\Nwith one Zaku?! That's some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Job John, can't you increase the speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not running well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The damage from the direct hit\Nit received the other day hasn't been fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just a Zaku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! The shaft is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine's running, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.73,0:10:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give much support from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right? Hang on, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind me!\NJust get Amuro out of the brig!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to promise to stay in bed, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Bright...\N- Sayla! Where have you been?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Hurry to the bridge!r to Amuro's cell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryu's been here, talking to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He says he'll take responsibility,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That meddling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take responsibility too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's F-36 type.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu did this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, for Ryu's sake as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Zeons! I'll get you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There're more of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Trojan Horse.\NJust as we planned, you can't move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the tenacity\Nof the Ramba Ral team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Numbers 1, 2, and 3 show no increase\Nin power output!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter! Mirai! Let's take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!\NSayla, will the Gundam be able to launch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he should be ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam, are you ready to launch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mechanics are all Injured,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- As long as It moves, It's fine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to launch In the Core Fighter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of the repairs, Gundam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:13:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,White Base may be taking off soon.\NAll right, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No problem!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! Mirai! The Core Fighter is launching!\NAll right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.04,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll happen even if I veto it. Right, Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no chance without the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna leave their graves behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the same guy I was before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't back down! I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just lay down the bed\Nand launch the Gundam parts?! It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The procedure's in the manual,\Nbut I've never done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we do things on the White Base!\NI'll figure out the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's the one who's supposed to be\Na professional soldier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:13:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't mess with\Nthe White Base anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw, go give them a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to the starboard machine guns.\NYou can pull a trigger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you wear a helmet.\NOr else you'll lose your hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Guntank's broken?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mirai! Can't we get the White Base moving?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have no buoyancy!hot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Launch the Gundam parts?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did Amuro say that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! You mustn't get out of bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your injuries are worse than all of ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sickness and injury won't matter\Nif the White Base goes down in flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! What are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta get the Guntank moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If the White Base wasn't stuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.96,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wouldn't have been able to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one so far, huh?\NI should've come out earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! We're ready to launch{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do it!\NThe Core Fighter's out of ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Launching Gundam B Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher, activated
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Fighter, change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch laser sensor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Roll 180 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Attitude okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Mr. Omur!\NLaunch A Parts as soon as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Launch position, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hit the Zaku from here,\Nbut the White Base will get damaged too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is hand-to-hand combat my only option?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...\NIs that thing trying to ram us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That must mean it's packed with explosives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to stop our charge?\NHow impudent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam can't hold it by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If it crashes into the Trojan Horse,\Nthe explosives will...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachi! Get the Gundam from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ms. Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Another, from above...?! Can I do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.74,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That Gundam took out two pilots at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect no less from the boy\Nwho caught my notice. However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I shoot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hit just the Magella Top!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,However thick\Nthe Gundam's armor may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...it won't hold up at this range.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion from the Gundam and Cargo\Nwill take out the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hamon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked you, dear boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Core Fighter! Who was piloting it...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! It's a hovercraft,\Nso if I just hit one engine...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any enemies still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The battle Is over, Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you and the Gundam all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.14,0:19:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was in that Core Fighter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay calm, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was Ryu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.45,0:20:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryu rammed the plane...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu's injured.\NThere's no way he could go into combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't joke around, Ms. Sayla...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault... I practically killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I didn't switch with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mr. Ryu wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Switch with me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have more experience than you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But It won't work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to think of ways{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Core Fighter can still be used!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get out of my way, rookie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have allowed\NMr. Ryu to launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Ryu! Are you going to be all right?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need all the fighting strength we can get!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I must have worried him\Ntoo much over Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not true. Right, Ms. Mirai?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's starting to change a lot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never mind me!out of the brig!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take responsibility.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu...! Mr. Ryu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.68,0:21:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's afraid of you,ild tiger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Funny, Isn't It?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was responsible for his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the one... I was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop that, Mr. Job John!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that way too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe even Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... It's everyone! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as Amuro says!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of our immaturity\Nthat Ryu died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And so many others were lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.14,0:22:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do\Nfrom now on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Ryu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you won't advise me anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.86,0:22:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is defeat Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And end the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.50,0:22:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright collapses after Ryu's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to take advantage,\NM'Quve launches a siege operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...quietly, and intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A mid-air docking during battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...finally puts Amuro in extreme danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam.\NNext episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trap of M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trap of M'Quve
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:54.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:09.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:14.18,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:18.81,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:24.19,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:28.77,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:39.08,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:54.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:09.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:14.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:18.81,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:24.19,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:28.77,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:39.08,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
